- Absolute script paths in the generated registry/workflow are intentional
  (runner cwd is the scratch worktree). Keep generation in walkthrough.sh / the
  test; do not commit a static registry with hardcoded paths.
- Low overall: reproduced end-to-end against the current binary with no engine edit.

